Package de.hu.gralog.graph.alg

This package defines all classes needed to implement algorithms in GraLog.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Algorithm This interface has to be implement by all GraLog algorithms.
AlgorithmResultListener  
 

Class Summary
AlgorithmResult This class basically serves as a container for AlgorithmResultContent's.
AlgorithmResultContent The class represents a content which is displayed as part of an AlgorithmResult.
AlgorithmResultContentTreeNode This class extends AlgorithmResultContent in order to form a tree of contents.
AlgorithmResultInteractiveContent  
Algorithms  
ChooseGraphPropertyDescriptor This class is a special PropertyDescriptor for properties of algorithms in GrALoG.
ChooseVertexPropertyDescriptor This class is a special PropertyDescriptor for properties of algorithms in GrALoG.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidPropertyValuesException This Exception is used to return errors concerning the values of properties for algorithms.
 

Package de.hu.gralog.graph.alg Description

This package defines all classes needed to implement algorithms in GraLog. Please refer to the documentation of Algorithm to see what needs to be done in order to implement an algorithm.
